OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780913124
OL,3,CManslaughter arrest after man found
OL,4,Cdead alongside number of dogs
OL,6,FA woman has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof manslaughter after a man was found
OL,8,Fdead in his home alongside a number of
OL,9,Fdogs.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to
OL,12,FCoachmans Drive, in West Derby in
OL,13,FLiverpool, at around 6.10pm on 5 June
OL,14,Ffollowing reports a man in his 70s had
OL,15,Fdied.
OL,17,FMerseyside Police say the death is
OL,18,Fbeing treated as unexplained and an
OL,19,Finvestigation to establish what
OL,20,Fhappened is on going.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
