OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780913124
OL,3,CManslaughter arrest after man found
OL,4,Cdead alongside number of dogs
OL,6,FA 55-year-old woman from West Derby
OL,7,Fhas been arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmanslaughter, carer ill-treat/wilfully
OL,9,Fneglect a person and causing
OL,10,Funnecessary suffering to an animal.
OL,12,FShe has been conditionally bailed
OL,13,Fpending further inquiries.
OL,15,FOfficers say they are also attempting
OL,16,Fto trace the man's next of kin and
OL,17,Fhave asked anyone who believes they
OL,18,Fmay know the person to get in touch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
