PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780913124
OL,3,CManslaughter arrest after man found
OL,4,Cdead alongside number of dogs
OL,6,FTemporary Detective Chief
OL,7,FSuperintendent Helen Bennett said:
OL,8,F"Our thoughts at this time are with
OL,9,Fthe family of the man who has sadly
OL,10,Fpassed way.
OL,12,F"As this matter is clearly in the very
OL,13,Fearly stages, we would ask people to
OL,14,Favoid speculating and allow us to
OL,15,Fcarry out our enquiries.
OL,17,F"Although we have arrested a person in
OL,18,Fconnection with the investigation, we
OL,19,Fare still appealing for anyone with
OL,20,Finformation to come forward.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
